## ⭐ Featured Work

*The three pieces I'd show you first if we only had five minutes.*

### 1. 🔍 [Multi-Outlet Daypart Collapse Analysis](./02-dashboard-collection/daypart-analysis)
End-to-end pipeline (Python ETL → PostgreSQL → Power BI) that uncovered a **61% afternoon revenue collapse** in one outlet — invisible in aggregate reports — with an estimated impact of **Rp 14M/month** and an actionable staffing + menu fix.
`PostgreSQL` `Window Functions` `Power BI` `Impact Quantification`

### 2. 📈 [Menu Engineering Matrix](./02-dashboard-collection/menu-engineering)
Classic popularity × contribution-margin analysis applied to café SKUs — with per-quadrant recommendations (reprice, reposition, retire) and a simulated profit impact. Built from real operational knowledge, not textbook assumptions.
`SQL` `Python` `Business Strategy`

### 3. 🧠 [Business Thinking Journal](./04-business-thinking-journal)
My differentiator: company case simulations where I pick a real business and reason through **which 3 KPIs actually matter and why**, what problem data can attack — and honestly, what data *can't* answer. This is how I'd think on my first week at your company.
`Business Sense` `KPI Design` `Epistemic Honesty`

